        "别让他俩闹拧了"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "擰"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "adjective",
      "meaning": "倔强，不驯服，固执。",
      "examples": [
        "拧脾气",
        "他这人挺拧的"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "擰"
    }
  ],
  "formations": [
